description: Are you looking for a spacious home in a hot neighborhood? Is a gas stove on your wish list? This one has it!  Fireplace? It has that too! Beautiful bay window, double doors on the primary suite, arched doorways, dead end street and curb appeal to add to the charm of this home! This is one you do not want to miss! Don't forget to check out the amazing, private and fenced backyard!

description: Looking for quality const?You have found it in this home!This is a JCB Urban well built home with lots of custom builder features.You will see the difference.Like new arts and crafts style home built by a custom builder in a historic Charlotte neighborhood.Large front and back covered porches perfect for entertaining.Private fenced in backyard with storage.Quick access to Uptown in one direction.Easy access to Charlotte restaurants and night life.Walking distances to Mint Museum,Briar Creek Greenway,coffee shops,restaurants and local brewery.Open floorplan with smooth,high ceilings.Craftsman details including trim work on baseboards and windows throughout entire home.Molding in main area.Kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steal appliances, great size pantry and island.Main BR with walk-in closet and in suite bath.Pull down attic stairs with tons of floored storage space. Beautiful site finished walnut stained hard wood floors in main area. Custom fit 2 1/2 in blinds throughout.

description: Hard to find 1 story with basement, on a cul-de-sac, situated on 1 acre.  A peaceful & private sanctuary, minutes from Charlotte. Rippling creek. Experience deer, hummingbirds, cardinals and owls, surrounded by a forest of hardwoods, dogwoods, camelia, jonquil and hydrangea. Charming kitchen with tumbled tile counters & backsplash, Frigidaire Professional stainless steel 5-burner gas range & gas oven; spacious breakfast area; a lovely living room & a newly added family room in 2017 – charming & comfortable. Relax and enjoy a beverage in the comfort of the screened porch.  Owner's suite features a spacious bedroom, tumbled tile counter in the bathroom & a walk-in closet.  And let’s not forget the basement – featuring the laundry, storage & workshop area. Well maintained! New roof 2017. New Hardi-plank siding 2017. New HVAC 2010. Septic pumping scheduled for June 8th. Generac instant backup power generator.  3 BRs, 2 BAs, 1,732 sf, 2 car carport.

description: Very hard to find 5 bedroom 3.5 bath home in the desirable Herons Pond Subdivision!!! This home boasts a very large open floorplan with plenty of room to entertain. You enter to find 2 office/dining/flex spaces as well as the spacious living room and kitchen and a half bath on the main level. Venture upstairs to discover the palatial loft area central to the 5 bedrooms and 3 baths. Home will need paint and flooring throughout and this is reflected in the price. Schedule your showing now so you don't miss this one.

description: Beautifully updated 4 bed 2 bath home in Charlotte. Fresh paint throughout. Updated lighting and plumbing fixtures. Brand new LVP and carpet. Open living room features a marble and slate fireplace. Kitchen has been fully renovated with refinished cabinets, granite countertops, tile backsplash, and SS appliances. Bathrooms have updated vanities, mirrors, new tubs, and toilets. Primary bath has a tiled shower and porcelain tile. Fenced in backyard. Close to shopping and restaurants. 10 mins to NoDa.

description: BRAND NEW CONSTRUCTION. This beautiful custom build home features a open floor plan with a bonus room that can easily be built into a fourth bedroom by either the buyer or by the builder for a small pre negotiated price by just adding a door and a closet where there's already a space allocated for it. This home was built by craftsman who took there time because they value quality work with only the best material's inside and out from the exterior self cleaning paint architectural shingles, double gable to the interior LVP flooring, bathroom tile and granite counter tops. No cheap cabinets in this house these expensive beauties are craftsman built and finished. This property is conveniently located to everything. Less than a mile to Walmart and other brand name shopping outlets. Best of all its less than three miles from 485. So not matter where you work or have to go this home at this low price is a deal that wont last long.- Home is being professionally photographed Monday.

description: LOCATION! THIS IS IT! According to CMS, this home will be served by the new Palisades High School. This beautiful, 2-story, 4bed, and 2.5 bath home sits in Greycrest, minutes away from Rivergate shopping, dining, Atrium hospital, and more! Trees around the house provide large amounts of shade and privacy. The rocking chair front porch will be your favorite spot- Already equipped with a swing. Large PR bedroom with dual sink, garden tub, and walk-in closet in bath. 3 other well-sized rooms and a full bath upstairs as well. The home is equipped with a newer tankless water heater. Enjoy the day on the back deck, looking out into the large, fenced-in yard, perfect for those with energetic pets. Host family and friends by the backyard fire pit or grill out on the deck.  The gas line is already installed. Current rental cap in the neighborhood. Hurry this beauty will not be here long!

description: This 2 story home has new flooring and paint throughout.  Located at the end of a cul-de-sac with a large fully fenced back yard. Upstairs has 2 good size secondary bedrooms and a primary bedroom with wonderfully tall ceilings.  All of this in a community that is centrally located and not far from Northlake Mall, Center City Charlotte, Huntersville and the airport.  Don't miss your chance to call this gem home.

description: Wonderful large home in desirable Kingstree community.  4 bedrooms including large primary and three spacious secondary bedrooms, 2.5 baths.  Kitchen with ample cabinetry open to breakfast and living room.  Dishwasher, disposal, electric range / oven, and new microwave. Refrigerator is included.  This home has a formal dining room as well as kitchen breakfast area eating.  Nice office, playroom, or schoolroom on main level, right next to half bath.  New Hot water heater 2021. Primary bedroom has a vaulted ceiling and walk in closet.  Master bath features two vanities, garden tub and separate shower, toilet compartment. Upstairs laundry room with shelves.  Garage has some built ins and automatic opener, also keypad entry.  Great big open back yard is fenced and level for all your outdoor entertainment and activities.  Security system, window treatments included.  Community pool, clubhouse, playground and walking trails.  Central to Charlotte and everything you need.

description: Amazing opportunity to be in an established South Charlotte neighborhood with amenities!  Bishops Ridge is a hidden gem -- close to Southpark, Uptown and Matthews. Ideal location yet under $400,000!  Excellent chance for a buyer to personalize with their own updates. Open floorplan with the primary bedroom on the main floor. Downstairs has a large secondary bedroom and another room that has a closet and access to a bathroom. There is also a bonus room in the basement. The deck can be accessed from the great room and primary bedroom. The lot is private with mature trees and landscaping. The kitchen has heart of pine flooring. Large private deck that is partically covered.  This house is super cute and ready for a new owner to personalize!   Home is being sold as is.

description: Charming ranch style home in Wedgewood North on a low traffic cul-de-sac street. Conveniently located just 10 minutes to Uptown Charlotte and 10 minutes to Lake Norman.  Fantastic large, flat backyard and nice landscaping.

description:
THE PROPERTY IS TENANT OCCUPIED, PLEASE DO NOT DISTURB TENANT. 

Stunning  3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, with bonus room that can be used as a bedroom/office/playroom. Washer and dryer hookups are located upstairs along with all the bedrooms. First floor features an oversized living room, with a fireplace, formal dining room, breakfast area, and an open kitchen equipped with all appliances.  there is a 2-car garage that leads directly into the kitchen. A quaint front porch and back patio area perfect for entertaining.  HOA offers an Olympic-sized swimming pool, tennis courts, an outdoor playground area, and a clubhouse, where regular social functions are held for neighborhood residents. home nestled in the neighborhood of "Calloway Plantation". Conveniently located off of Margaret Wallace Road near E. Independence Blvd and close to W.T. Harris, this home is located near many shopping centers and restaurants and conveniently located close to highways and just 20 minutes from uptown Charlotte.

description: OFFERS DUE AT NOON ON MAY 24, 2022.  Full brick home on a beautiful .87 acre level lot.  The 1858 square foot home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  You will love the extra large laundry room. The living room/dining room has updated windows.  Additional 217 square footage is found in the bright sunroom with its own heating and cooling unit.  The sunroom overlooks the huge fenced backyard that houses a detached garage/workshop and shed.  Outside the sunroom is a deck for lounging or grilling.  There is also a gardening spot in the back.  Under the carport is a storage room with shelving.  Home needs some updating but listing price reflects that. The home is located in an established neighborhood and is conveniently located to I-485, the Whitewater Center and the outlet mall.  Come make this one your forever home.  Home is being sold as-is.  The seller will not make any repairs.

New HAVAC system and New Roof

description: Fantastic find in Charlotte, NC!  This home is an all brick ranch and is located on a corner lot.  It is nestled up against a wooded area that allows you to be embraced by the feel of privacy, yet you're minutes from 485, CLT Douglas Airport, shopping, entertainment, and a plethora of dining options!  This home has so much to offer! Large yard, fabulous floor plan, one level living, large two car garage, and more.  The Owner(s) are selling this home that includes two adjoining parcels; one wooded lot & another lot with a 2 car garage/shop that has a Flex space of 350+ sq ft!  With all 3 lots combined you will be living on 1.5+/- acres in CLT!! Unique opportunity to make this house your home.  Make an appointment today to view this property & get more details! Please note, the Tax Value reflects all three Parcels' Tax Value(s) and the acreage reflects all three Tax Parcels together.

description: Great opportunity to own a home in the Houston Farms neighborhood with NO HOA!!! A well maintained split floor plan, this 3 bed 2.5 bath home features a converted two-car garage, covered front porch, walk-in pantry, and LARGE office that could easily be converted to a 4th bedroom! Huge lot and backyard for the area! Spacious primary En-Suite with vaulted ceilings and his and hers closets. Ideal location that is close to food, shopping, the PNC Pavilion and quick access to Interstate 485. Add your personal touch and this home is ready to be your forever home! Come get it before its GONE!

description: Full brick ranch with beautifully landscaped yard! Single story living at its best! Front entryway hosts large double closets for plenty of storage. Your main living space features crown moulding throughout and a dining room with pocket door that can be used as an office if needed. Kitchen is light and bright with stainless steel appliances and a large bay window. Living room has brand new carpet and has a gas fireplace perfect for cool, winter evenings. Spacious primary bedroom has large walkin closet and private updated en-suite. 2 more secondary bedrooms share and updated full bath and have double closes. Home features sunroom that is fully wired and finished to allow for year round enjoyment of the beautiful private yard. Large deck is freshly painted and leads to the just cleaned Jacuzzi hot tub w/brand new cover. New roof in 2020 and HVAC in 2019. Foundation is a partial basement which is perfect for extra storage or workshop. All of this with no HOA!

description:
Come see this charming home in the Quiet and mature Scotsborough subdivision in North Charlotte!
 Walk into an open living room with vaulted ceilings and a cozy gas log fireplace!
 Spacious Kitchen and dining area! The Primary suite is located on the ground floor and has it's own private walk-in closet. New HVAC 2021. Large Manicured Trees' cover the Front Lot! Lovely Landscaped Lawn! Very Low traffic Street!

 Easy access to I-77 / I-85 and the Charlotte uptown and  amenities! Minutes from the University area and Concord Mills Outlet Mall!

description: 4 bedroom/2.5 bathroom home in desirable Davis Meadows!  On the main level you will find a formal living room, a spacious eat-in kitchen has an abundance of cabinets for plenty of storage and stainless steel appliances. The living room has a nice fireplace.  The upstairs has a large primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and a full master bathroom with a separate tub and shower.  The three additional bedrooms upstairs are spacious and there is a full hall bathroom for convenience.  The laundry closet is located on the second level.  The backyard is spacious and perfect to summer cook-outs and entertaining! Close to I-77 and uptown Charlotte.  Don't miss out on this one!

description: This adorable corner lot bungalow located in historic Druid Hills awaits its new owner. The dining and living room sit directly across from each other, making it the perfect entertainment space. Kitchen equipped w/stainless steel appl's & granite countertops. Laundry room w/ plenty of cabinetry for storage. Primary suite tucked away in the back of the home w/ walk-in closet & ensuite bath w/ dual sinks. Upstairs-2 add'l BDRs & a full BA w/dual sinks   Hardwoods in main areas of the home. Rocking chair front porch to enjoy the summer breeze. Exterior storage room. Property located next to Druid Hills Community Neighborhood Park. Plans for the park are underway to include a playground, covered pavilion w/ restrooms, renovated basketball court, etc. NO INVESTORS, CANNOT BE USED AS RENTAL PROPERTY OR 2ND HOME. PROPERTY MUST BE OWNER OCCUPIED, PRIMARY RESIDENCE. HOUSEHOLD INCOME  AT OR BELOW 80% OF THE AREA MEDIAN INCOME(SEE AMI CHART ATTACHED).Contact list agent with any questions.
